Use case: View all applications deployed via Helm.

5ï¸âƒ£ Create a Helm Chart
helm create mychart
Use case: Generate a pre-built chart structure to customize your own application deployment.

6ï¸âƒ£ Dry Run Before Deployment
helm install myapp ./mychart --dry-run
Use case: Verify templates before pushing to production.

7ï¸âƒ£ Pull a Chart for Review
helm pull bitnami/nginx --untar
Use case: Download and inspect chart files locally.
